data.description: Under market value and priced well below new construction! Beautiful, bold, better than new (2yr old) Kapalua villa in Magnolia Golf Villas. Artist and Collector inspired home. Soaring 10 and 12 foot ceilings with tray and crown moldings. Eight foot doors, huge windows and acres of sliding glass doors that lead out to the oversized screened and ceramic tiled lanai. Very private with wooded views. Granite throughout and the best cabinets you will ever have. Soft close cabinets and drawers with under cabinet lighting and stainless steel appliances. Trouble free luxury plank flooring. No carpets to worry about here. Master bathroom with walk in shower, water closet and walk in closet. Guest bedroom with bath and pocket door to close off for privacy. And yes, we have window treatments. The den/office can be used for all your creative needs. Maintenance free living, no yard work, no outside painting. Community swimming pool that you do not have to personally care for. There is an oversized one car garage. Never any smoking and never any pets. Very particular homeowners. Relax and enjoy your freedom in this very secure community.  Sun n Lake is home to two championship golf courses , with the Islandview restaurant, tennis courts, pickleball and basketball courts, playground, community center and dog park, not to mention most of your medical facilities and hospital are all within the neighborhood.  Come see why everyone wants to live in Sun n Lake!
